{"tid":376753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 天文台在下午4時10分山泥傾瀉警告","createTime":"2017-08-27T08:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T09:33:40.000Z","uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e52f34d95d5ba87ddcf029e0af6200aedd4908ac","tid":376753,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:19:57.000Z","msg":"山泥傾瀉警告<br />\n<br />\n香港天文台在2017年8月27日下午4時10分發出有關山泥傾瀉之特別報告：<br />\n<br />\n香港天文台已經發出山泥傾瀉警告，請勿行近斜坡或擋土牆。<br />\n<br />\n駕車人士應該避免駛經山坡地區或豎有山泥傾瀉警告牌的路段。<br />\n<br />\n如你察覺有山泥傾瀉跡象，應即遠離該處及通知警方。<br />\n<br />\n以上天氣稿由天文台於2017年08月27日16時10分發出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc9897d8781f632bb5e37c6d92aecc2ba4f292de","tid":376753,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:24:01.000Z","msg":"好似依家好少出呢個"},{"pid":"d67d6cce66e0a0af5fdb6107dde95c40edda796e","tid":376753,"uid":131423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:29:37.000Z","msg":"香港斜坡都mark哂number，落哂石屎泥釘<br />\n冇乜可能仲會有大型山泥傾瀉<br />\n郊野公園入面個d另計"},{"pid":"28b683ca2389a2c8392798ce2cd45e47acd306e5","tid":376753,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:31:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港斜坡都mark哂number，落哂石屎泥釘<br />\n冇乜可能仲會有大型山泥傾瀉<br />\n郊野公園入面個d另計</blockquote><br />\n有D仲做緊斜坡工程，係高危區域 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94a4a54ca0d6a777c775e273ad6509c9a368c27","tid":376753,"uid":22210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:23:13.000Z","msg":"好耐冇聽過"},{"pid":"dc2ccc595ee99083369cafb7c9d5d486661dd455","tid":376753,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:29:38.000Z","msg":"連續落雨打風 啲抓緊山坡泥土既樹就吹到連根拔起"},{"pid":"833b03f37f89bcd53e89f8deaf5836bf50dae9f1","tid":376753,"uid":23271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:33:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似依家好少出呢個</blockquote><br />\n